spin around and then fall.

521
00:18:55.117 --> 00:18:56.542
- Oh. boy. Okay.
- Oh. God. oh. God.

522
00:18:56.694 --> 00:18:58.230
I'm in the
moment. I'm in the moment.

523
00:18:58.254 --> 00:18:59.506
- I'm in the moment...
- Oh. God...

524
00:18:59.530 --> 00:19:01.197
Now!

525
00:19:06.295 --> 00:19:09.388
